{"tid":2322391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[理性討論] 侵Trump既Endgame究竟係乜？","createTime":"2020-12-12T09:47:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T06:28:46.000Z","uid":14503,"like":16,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"5770f6da54d8ebd02d2a19ab62dcb9d6184bea11","tid":2322391,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:47:35.000Z","msg":"今日美國聯邦最高法院以 7：2 reject 左 Texas 既訴訟， 連呢個咁明顯嘅違憲訴訟都可以唔處理 基本上其他三條法律線都會無功而還可以宣布死亡。<br />\n<br />\n美國已經去到一個地步唔係講侵侵既個人輸贏而係講美國憲法仲得唔得倒彰顯，主流媒體同幾個tech giants既壟斷過大已經威脅到美國既言論自由， 紅州同藍州嘅對抗撕裂， 加州內部分裂， 共和黨放風要組聯合政府，FBI,CIA 唔聽總統命令， 雖然拜登家族醜聞浮面但主流媒體繼續洗地試途幫佢解畫，藍營對內亦都冇諗住之後會解決ANTIFI BLM 問題所以呢度好快都會爆煲，拜登對外實會討好中國， 唔會再好似pompeo咁強硬， 新嘅制裁應該唔會再有， 之前嘅制裁應該會慢慢lift up.<br />\n<br />\n究竟侵侵係餘下一個月仲有咩牌可以扭轉乾坤？<br />\n即使唔係為咗連任，只係為咗美國佢仲可以做乜？<br />\n佢陣營既Endgame到底係點？"},{"pid":"4424b994a17af3e3d82c8f9e7da0b25cb12690c3","tid":2322391,"uid":14503,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T11:33:56.000Z","msg":"冇人討論？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad5a1d62414485e8f722df678befff57c041dc0","tid":2322391,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T11:36:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08415117759e9d5ead77f8f91b430f276de31c07","tid":2322391,"uid":324629,"like":17,"dislike":4,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T11:37:32.000Z","msg":"侵侵最尾都係要輸喺deep state嘅手上，好唔甘心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c44d8ccd20938403cc4008883abf9743dc60cac4","tid":2322391,"uid":202354,"like":3,"dislike":6,"