庭覺得隔離枱枱麻雀，枱嗰四個自己打，旁觀者不得依牙鬆弶，德州自己打返自己隔離嗰枱。"},{"pid":"afa2adaa26ced41dbed7b68a1225f7829eca0f62","tid":2322391,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"430f84b90176ed1e470f490fdb1447e9d2d5ef45","tid":2322391,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"a2bdc75f907f39b51bc248c4aebf7f5720c68766","tid":2322391,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"474b6034363b84dd246ca9cf80ff4098f57e67fc","tid":2322391,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T14:29:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同加拿大搞左膠聯邦呀笨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T16:08:26.000Z","msg":"加拿大君主立憲制，就算加拿大左膠，佢君主立憲嘅地位都幾受支持，唔似澳洲。<br />\n<br />\n所以見唔到美國嘅洲會想同加拿大聯合"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T16:09:23.000Z","msg":"加拿大有君主？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T16:20:32.000Z","msg":"加拿大正名係加拿大自治領<br />\n英國國會通過1937年西敏法令，確立自治領同英國喺國際社會同等地位，英國不會再為自治領立法。<br />\n<br />\n自治領啫係獨立自主嘅&rdquo;殖民地&rdquo;，君主係同一個事頭婆<br />\n澳洲、新西蘭亦然"},{"pid":"2767bcb1c13c6f0be085f252a7dc8651f4b7aed7","tid":2322391,"uid":54437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"430f84b90176ed1e470f490fdb1447e9d2d5ef45","tid":2322391,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"a2bdc75f907f39b51bc248c4aebf7f5720c68766","tid":2322391,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"474b6034363b84dd246ca9cf80ff4098f57e67fc","tid":2322391,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T14:29:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同加拿大搞左膠聯邦呀笨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T16:08:26.000Z","msg":"加拿大君主立憲制，就算加拿大左膠，佢君主立憲嘅地位都幾受支持，唔似澳洲。<br />\n<br />\n所以見唔到美國嘅洲會想同加拿大聯合"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T16:09:23.000Z","msg":"加拿大有君主？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T16:27:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g4F968dFp4s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dg4F968dFp4s&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcn6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=60a3f753\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g4F968dFp4s</a><br />\n英女皇"},{"pid":"c0bb69417d71e59a7e6760b428e50bc28f993a6a","tid":2322391,"uid":4722,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T16:44:56.000Z","msg":"為什麼到處聲稱選舉舞弊、到了法院內卻說不是在起訴舞弊？<br />\n<br />\n一來，自然是因為根本沒證據、或所謂的證據其實不是證據。<br />\n<br />\n二者，則是因為Federal Rules of Civil Procedure（聯邦民事訴訟規則，FRCP）。<br />\n<br />\n根據FRCP Rule 9(b)，要聲稱舞弊／詐騙（fraud），則必須要陳述舞弊的細節（&quot;state with particularity&quot;）。這項規則的存在有三個原因︰(1)提供被告足夠時間的通知去辯護、以及避免原告為求搜證而隨便起訴；(2)保護被聲稱詐騙的被告的名聲；(3) 防止原告在沒有任何事實根據下單方面對法院、訴訟雙方及社會構成巨大社會及經濟成本（Kearns v Ford Motor Co., 567 F3d 1120, 1125 [9th Cir 2009]）。<br />\n<br />\n也就是說，一宗聲稱舞弊的聯邦官司的最低要求是要提供足夠的particularity（細節） - 例如基本的「四個W一個H」&ldquo;the who, what, when, where, and how&rdquo;（Vess v Ciba-Geigy Corp. USA, 317 F3d 1097, 1106 [9th Cir 2003]）。<br />\n<br />\n例如，假設我要到聯邦法院起訴我太太欺騙了我的感情，則我必須要在起訴書中指出她在哪裡、何時、用什麼方法欺騙了我的什麼感情。<br />\n<br />\n問題是，Trump陣營不但沒有證據，就連particularity也沒有。Trump陣營在賓州起訴書中本來有聲稱有關舞弊的陳述，但後來卻在修正版本中大量刪除了有關主張。<br />\n<br />\n在聆訊中，Giuliani首先聲稱是在起訴舞弊(2:14:49)，而當法官指出FRCP Rule 9(b)對起訴舞弊的particularity要求後(2:15:50)，Giuliani又改正說並非在起訴舞弊(2:16:42)。<br />\n<br />\n結果正如之前所說，就是dismissed with prejudice。"},{"pid":"55bae34d0afb617b0b59e3ee3f5a506fe4f502f6","tid":2322391,"uid":55658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7714dddc7671f50a87ce044e7a3f3b03a310d41f","tid":2322391,"uid":197563,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"a4b656e8c3dfe8682ccb954aee4aae5bed948cc1","tid":2322391,"uid":55658,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:53:05.000Z","msg":"其實trump唔會end game，但相當有機會會分裂成以加州、紐約為首嘅舊美國，同以德州為首嘅新美國<br />\n然後隨著一班科技、工業企業撤往德州，最後美國再次統一"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T14:13:57.000Z","msg":"咁搞法libtard可以分到幾多地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CghYzZx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCghYzZx.jpg&h=4fe9173f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T17:28:53.000Z","msg":"大國嚟㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"550c1c60753859ee261f95f216e7fc6d25d61994","tid":2322391,"uid":55658,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3aea438ae92c48fe23aff876f72ea14dae6ade13","tid":2322391,"uid":268537,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b17546ba8d35d28ac3d5a59b9731c2e4848839f0","tid":2322391,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f6a947cf2e5d3cb0c0f33b29a0da8cbd9e72646","tid":2322391,"uid":325716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T14:04:36.000Z","msg":"連任唔到<br />\n只需要令全國陷入矛盾<br />\n拜登上場自然咩都做唔成<br />\n商人睇嘅利益係長遠<br />\n拜登實做唔完<br />\n賀錦麗自然會令民主黨內部分裂<br />\n共和黨傾定下屆邊個做總統"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T14:05:29.000Z","msg":"咁香港又等4年？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T14:19:11.000Z","msg":"天助自助者<br />\n想要人投資就要證明自己價值先<br />\n以色列都係靠自己然後先有美國幫<br />\n<br />\n就算侵贏香港都唔會即時有民主自由<br />\n最多係制裁同局部軍事衝突製造機會<br />\n所以香港人都係要證明自己能力先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T17:30:13.000Z","msg":"無錯，所以我哋要證明我哋嘅價值"},{"pid":"9af56cb54e488b657b2d4ac